Class SessionProxyState

java.lang.Object
  vista.set.Session
      vista.set.SessionProxyState
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, GroupManager, Named
public abstract class SessionProxyState
extends Session

The state pattern for use on proxy so that once initialized there is no overhead for checking for initialization. It does this by delegating to proxy object if uninitialized and to the actual object once initialized...
